OL,3,CBereaved mum 'reliving own tragedy'
OL,4,Cafter open water deaths
OL,6,FA bereaved mum is calling for
OL,7,F"consistent and concise" water safety
OL,8,Fteaching in schools, following the
OL,9,Fdeaths of multiple young people across
OL,10,Fthe country over the bank holiday
OL,11,Fweekend.
OL,13,FBeckie Ramsay lost her son Dylan when
OL,14,Fhe drowned while swimming in open
OL,15,Fwater in July 2011, and now runs the
OL,16,F'Doing it for Dylan' campaign, pushing
OL,17,Ffor water safety to be added to the
OL,18,FNational Curriculum.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
