PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1779991869
OL,3,CBereaved mum 'reliving own tragedy'
OL,4,Cafter open water deaths
OL,6,FHer calls follow the discovery of two
OL,7,Fbodies in two different locations
OL,8,Facross the North West, with a third
OL,9,Fperson fighting for their life in
OL,10,Fhospital after getting into difficulty
OL,11,Fin water.
OL,13,F"It just takes me back to the day that
OL,14,Fit happened to me. I just relive their
OL,15,Fnightmare, the people who have lost
OL,16,Ftheir lives, every single tragedy that
OL,17,Fwe see is like reliving my own
OL,18,Ftragedy," she said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
