FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1779991869
OL,3,CBereaved mum 'reliving own tragedy'
OL,4,Cafter open water deaths
OL,6,FIt comes after a number of teenagers
OL,7,Fdrowned across the country in open
OL,8,Fwater incidents over the bank holiday
OL,9,Fweekend.
OL,11,FCheshire Police confirmed a body has
OL,12,Fbeen found in the search for a 17-year-
OL,13,Fold boy who went missing while
OL,14,Fswimming in open water in Pickmere
OL,15,FLake in Northwich, Cheshire.
OL,17,FA body has also been found after a
OL,18,Fboy, 12, got into difficulty while
OL,19,Fswimming in the River Ribble in
OL,20,FRibchester.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1779991869
OL,3,CBereaved mum 'reliving own tragedy'
OL,4,Cafter open water deaths
OL,6,FA girl, 15, is in critical condition
OL,7,Fat Alder Hey Children's Hospital after
OL,8,Fentering the water at Formby Beach,
OL,9,FMerseyside.
OL,11,FBeckie, from Lancashire, said some
OL,12,Ffriends and family of the young people
OL,13,Fwho died have already reached out to
OL,14,Fher for support.
OL,16,FShe said: "This is a never ending
OL,17,Fthing for me, the more people that
OL,18,Ffind me, the more people that want
OL,19,Fsupport or advice, which I'm happy to
OL,20,Fgive but it is very very draining when
OL,21,Fit's continual.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1779991869
OL,3,CBereaved mum 'reliving own tragedy'
OL,4,Cafter open water deaths
OL,6,F"I hate summer. I hate the summer
OL,7,Fmonths because I know what I'm about
OL,8,Fto hear, with families going through
OL,9,Fwhat my family went through and that's
OL,10,Fall I can foresee."
OL,12,FCharity body RNLI is also warning
OL,13,Fpeople to be aware of cold water shock.
OL,15,F"While the air temperature is warm,
OL,16,Fthe seas are still cold and cold water
OL,17,Fshock remains a very real risk," a
OL,18,Fspokesperson said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1779991869
OL,3,CBereaved mum 'reliving own tragedy'
OL,4,Cafter open water deaths
OL,6,FThe organisation said this can lead to
OL,7,Fhyperventilation, a spike in heart
OL,8,Frate and blood pressure as the body
OL,9,Freacts to cold water. In the worst
OL,10,Fcases, even competent swimmers can
OL,11,Fdrown as their bodies cannot cope with
OL,12,Fthe change in temperature.
OL,14,FThe spokesperson continued: "With many
OL,15,Fschool children enjoying half term,
OL,16,Fthe lifesaving charity is urging
OL,17,Feveryone to stay safe."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
