FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1779991869
OL,3,CBereaved mum 'reliving own tragedy'
OL,4,Cafter open water deaths
OL,6,FBeckie has been campaigning for
OL,7,Fincreased water safety training 15
OL,8,Fyears in July. Her sixth petition to
OL,9,Fget it put on the National Curriculum
OL,10,Fgot enough signatures to go to
OL,11,Fparliament, and is due to be
OL,12,Fimplemented in schools from September
OL,13,F2026.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1779991869
OL,3,CBereaved mum 'reliving own tragedy'
OL,4,Cafter open water deaths
OL,6,FShe said: "My job as a parent is to
OL,7,Fmake sure it is actually put it place.
OL,8,FI need to make sure it's exactly the
OL,9,Fsame across the board, so every child
OL,10,Flearns the same, because sending mixed
OL,11,Fmessages to different child aren't
OL,12,Fgood, we need to make sure the
OL,13,Finformation is consistent and concise.
OL,15,F"It shouldn't be a postcode lottery as
OL,16,Fto whether you receive water safety or
OL,17,Fyou learn to swim. It shouldn't depend
OL,18,Fon where you live but unfortunately
OL,19,Fthat's how it is at the moment."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
