PN,39909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1779991869
OL,3,CBereaved mum 'reliving own tragedy'
OL,4,Cafter open water deaths
OL,6,FFigures from the National Water Safety
OL,7,FForum show more people drowned inland
OL,8,Fthan on the coast in 2025, making it
OL,9,Fthe seventh consecutive year.
OL,11,FBeckie said: "I think there's less
OL,12,Fdrownings on the coast than inland is
OL,13,Fbecause they've got the RNLI that go
OL,14,Fout and rescue, we don't really have
OL,15,Fmuch for inland - we have to ring the
OL,16,Ffire service - so our swift water
OL,17,Frescue teams are quite often not on
OL,18,Four doorsteps and that makes it really
OL,19,Fquite difficult."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
